				<div class="postbody">
				part of the punishment of a prision is to take away the prisoner's freedom of choice &amp; individual expression. Reguests for vegetarian meals have often been denied (without strong religious support) because they dont want any individuals to feel special. Giving them a choice of what productive thing to do is unlikely. Prision isn't a summer camp where you get to chose which arts and crafts you'll do this week.<br />
